&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the voice of the customer, advocating for user and business needs throughout product delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with senior product leaders to define product strategy, priorities, and delivery plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate workshops focused on discovery, requirements gathering, process mapping, ideation, prioritization, and solution definition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather, analyze, and document business requirements from client stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, refine, and maintain product backlogs, user stories, acceptance criteria, and release priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate fully in Agile ceremonies including backlog refinement, sprint planning, reviews, retrospectives, and other product delivery activities.&lt;/li&gt;
