&lt;li&gt;Build trusted relationships with clients through thoughtful communication, collaboration, and problem solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify risks, assumptions, dependencies, and opportunities early, helping teams make informed decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to product roadmaps and release planning alongside senior product leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Mindgrub Account Managers and Project Managers to ensure successful client engagements and software delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
