&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A source of consistency, reliability, and expertise within the Project Management Office (PMO), the Senior Project Manager is an experienced project leader and facilitator in all respects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Mindgrub, the Senior Project Manager goes above and beyond “on-time, on-budget, and on-scope” to become a true stakeholder in project success. They facilitate day-to-day priorities with energy and confidence. Senior Project Managers deftly know when and how to adjust their communication and management style when relaying direction based on the needs of a multi-disciplinary internal team of strategy, creative, and technology partners. They are the team’s champion throughout the entire project life cycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
